message: "If you use this software or architecture in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "EduRAG — Dual RAG Educativo (D-RAG-E)"
abstract: >
  EduRAG is a SaaS platform implementing the Dual RAG Educativo (D-RAG-E)
  architecture — a two-tier hierarchical Retrieval-Augmented Generation system
  for sovereign AI integration in national education systems. RAG Layer 1
  grounds responses in ministerial curricula; RAG Layer 2 personalises narrative
  per institution based on adopted textbooks. Compliant with EU AI Act,
  GDPR, and Italian MIM 2025 Guidelines.
